00:52:21.639 --> 00:52:27.080
you get things like your classic biomarkers, like body mass index, blood pressure, blood

00:52:27.080 --> 00:52:35.080
cholesterol, tumour size, et cetera. But then when it comes to measures of how much pain people feel,

00:52:36.760 --> 00:52:41.959
it's a lot less clear-cut how you measure that. And, you know, you might say it's a lot more

00:52:41.959 --> 00:52:50.520
